Package: halos-ublox-config
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gpsd-clients
Description: u-blox GNSS receiver auto-configuration for marine use
 Configures u-blox GNSS receivers connected via UART for marine use.
 Runs on every boot to ensure correct configuration, since ROM-based
 u-blox modules (such as the MAX-M8Q) cannot persist settings without
 a backup battery.
 .
 Configuration applied:
  * 10 Hz update rate (100 ms measurement interval)
  * Sea dynamic model (optimized for marine navigation)
  * 115200 bps baud rate
